These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, rose
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, siglo, montecristo
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the swisher-smoker and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Flower          | orchid      | daisy        | rose     |
| Cigar         | montecristo | siglo | swisher    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Beverage         | fanta  | hot-chocolate      | mirinda    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, december
City: berlin, miami, hannover
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
7. the person traveling to hannover is between the person watching disaster movies and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Beverage           | milk    | soy-milk | cola |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| Birthday           | december  | march   | april     |
| City         | miami | hannover       | berlin   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, oliveros, chaman
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, december
There are 3 different nationalities: french, egyptian, turkish
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the french##1
2. the chaman-smoker is the turkish##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the prince-smoker is between the person watching adventure movies and the turkish##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar          | chaman | prince | oliveros |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Birthday           | may       | april   | december    |
| Nationality     | turkish      | french   | egyptian |

