.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, december, november
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, indie, house
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, mystery
There 3 different types of food: apple, apricot, radish
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the fan of house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating radish##1
6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating radish##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Birthday         | december  | september       | november |
| Music-Genre           | house     | indie      | electronic   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | mystery     |
| Food   | apple      | radish   | apricot     |

