.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, crime
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, subway, train
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, salsa, soul
3 different games are played: monopoly, domino, bridge
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Movie-Genre      | crime     | animation   | martial-arts         |
| Transport           | airplane | subway | train |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | salsa   | pop            |
| Game   | domino   | bridge  | monopoly         |

