.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, snowmobile
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, photographer, social-worker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, cricket
3 different games are played: domino, poker, canasta
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the photographer and the person driving the airplane##2
2. the person playing domino is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Transport          | snowmobile    | quad-bike     | airplane |
| Job           | photographer | social-worker | doctor      |
| Sport   | cricket      | lacrosse       | baseball    |
| Game   | poker      | domino         | canasta     |

