The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, zombie
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, ritmeester, alhambra
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, colombian, british
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in the middle##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the colombian##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the bongani-smoker is between the colombian and the person who's sport is baseball##2
7. the british is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport          | baseball | volleyball | sailing |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action    | zombie |
| Cigar   | ritmeester  | bongani   | alhambra    |
| Nationality     | british   | dutch       | colombian |

