2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
7. the havana-smoker is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee    | soy-milk  |
| Cigar         | swisher        | havana   | bongani   |
| Sport   | rugby       | baseball    | climbing |
| Flower     | orchid          | tulip | poppy       |

