4. the person playing snooker is the person who growsrose##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
