3 different games are played: poker, domino, chess
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, puzzles, drawing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, disaster
1. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the person playing chess is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
