.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, coral, orange
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, car, bus
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, cottage
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the cottage house is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes blue and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Color      | orange       | coral   | blue |
| Transport   | bike | bus     | car |
| House           | gothic-revival      | cape-cod | cottage    |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | soccer     | biathlon |

