.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, jazz, blues
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, blood-red, coral
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, september, december
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, trike
1. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre           | classical | jazz   | blues |
| Color   | azure  | blood-red    | coral    |
| Birthday         | september    | august | december   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | trike     | airplane  |

