3 different pets are kept: dog, snake, rat
1. the american is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the snake is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday         | october    | june   | november      |
| Movie-Genre           | superhero | scientific    | mystery |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine | turkish      |
| Pet         | rat         | snake   | dog     |

