.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-16::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, february
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, epic, family
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, chef, manager
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, ebony, grey
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the manager##1
2. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes grey is the chef##1
5. the manager is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the manager##3
8. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Birthday          | may     | january   | february     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| Job   | chef | security-guard | manager    |
| Color     | grey  | pink   | ebony |

