There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, blue
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, bartender, librarian
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, train
1. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the ferret and the person driving the train##2
3. the mechanic is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Pet          | chinchilla     | goldfish | ferret   |
| Color         | blue   | mauve | ebony |
| Job   | librarian | bartender       | mechanic   |
| Transport     | train     | snowmobile  | taxi        |

