4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
6. the person playing domino is the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growslily is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
