2. the american is in an odd position##4
3. the palace house is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the turkish##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the dancer##3
6. the police-officer is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Job           | dancer  | police-officer | musician   |
| House   | art-deco | palace           | farmhouse      |
| Nationality           | american   | turkish          | french |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure    | drama           | fantasy |

 